CatDescriptText: Broadside on far wall advertises "Basketball, Bill Harris Tuxedo Pro. Stars, Renaissance Connelly Trade School, Wednesday, December 17, 1947"
TitMainTitle: Interior of Johnnie's Restaurant or Grill, with tin ceiling, two men behind counter and five people seated at counter, pin ball machines on the right side of image, and Johnnie's name is above the grill in raised letters
